ActiveState Perl (for CSE):

I didn't have luck installing later versions than 5.28.

----------------

For version 5.28:

At
https://platform.activestate.com/mernst/ActivePerl-5.28/distributions?new_project=true
I have two options:
 * Download .tar.gz file
 * Use the state tool.  (Don't do this.)

For downloading:
 * extract into ~/bin/install
 * Run: sh install.sh
   Directory for install: /homes/gws/mernst/bin/install/ActivePerl-5.28
   Do NOT install the HTML documentation; trying to do so fails.

